# This CLI does NOT read DB2i_* credentials itself — the server does, from the
# lite project's own .env (../../.env by default). You only need the variables below
# if your jar / tools / .env live somewhere non-standard.
#
# IBMI_MCP_HOME=/path/to/ibmi-mcp-server-lite
# IBMI_MCP_JAR=/path/to/ibmi-mcp-server-lite-0.1.0.jar
# IBMI_MCP_TOOLS=/path/to/tools/sample-tools.yaml   # or pass --tools on the CLI
# IBMI_MCP_ENV_FILE=/path/to/.env
